OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Flargely cloudy night for most with
OL,7,Fsome clear intervals. A few outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain possible in the west, and at
OL,9,Ftimes near the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy and mainly dry
OL,12,Fday. Chance of a little rain along the
OL,13,Feast coast at first, and elsewhere in
OL,14,Fthe afternoon.
